flowchart TD
    A[Start: Customer Initiates Onboarding] --> B[Customer Provides Personal & Business Info]
    B --> C[Document Upload <br/> (e.g., ID, Utility Bills, SSM Cert)]
    C --> D[Initial Screening <br/> (Blacklist, Sanctions, PEP Check)]
    D --> E{Customer Risk Rating}
    
    E -- Low Risk --> F[Proceed with Standard Due Diligence (SDD)]
    E -- Medium Risk --> G[Proceed with Customer Due Diligence (CDD)]
    E -- High Risk --> H[Proceed with Enhanced Due Diligence]
    
    F --> J[Verify Identity & Source of Funds]
    G --> J
    H --> J
    
    J --> K[Internal Compliance Review]
    K --> L{Compliance Approval?}
    
    L -- Approved --> M[Customer Account Created]
    L -- Rejected --> N[Notify Customer & Terminate Process]
    L -- Require More Info --> O[Request Additional Documents]
    O --> J

    M --> P[Welcome Email & Activation]
    P --> Q[Start Transaction Monitoring]
    Q --> R[End]
